KW  - Stock returns
KW  - Volatility
KW  - Scandinavia
KW  - EGARCH
AB  - New evidence is provided on price and volatility spillovers among the Danish, Norwegian, Swedish, and Finnish stock markets. The impact of good news (market advances) and bad news (market retreats) is described by a multivariate Exponential Generalized Autoregressive Conditionally Heteroskedastic (EGARCH) model. Volatility transmission is asymmetric, spillovers being more pronounced for bad than good news. Significant price and volatility spillovers exist but they are few in number.
